00:42:13.980 --> 00:42:15.900
it for us. And then they come back

00:42:15.900 --> 00:42:19.180
3x over time, 3x over budget, one third

00:42:19.180 --> 00:42:21.420
x quality. Why is software so hard? Why

00:42:21.420 --> 00:42:24.035
